{"tid":1453340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偽裝成對方人員，被捕後即場槍決！","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:33:21.000Z","uid":281328,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0e7d9c9b10a7563f53ecdc4f51f866637ce0e7d0","tid":1453340,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:54:37.000Z","msg":"戰爭有守則，偽裝成對方人員，被捕後即場槍決 ! <br />\n<br />\n1944年12月16日，盟軍登陸諾曼第後向德國逐步進逼，希特勒將所有兵力集中在比利時亞登地區，孤注一擲發動絕地反擊，展開突出部之役(Battle of Bulge)，並且派出由奧托.史科尼兹率領的一支受過特別訓練，並且能講流利美式英語的約160人特種部隊，穿上由戰俘身上獲得的美軍制服，裝備，武器及車輛，假扮成美軍，進行麒麟作戰(Operation Greif)。<br />\n<br />\n德軍特種部隊滲透到美軍後方，更改路標，制做混亂，誤導及趁機殺害毫無防範之小單位美軍。又佔據繆斯河上之橋樑，保障德軍進攻通道無阻，其後德軍反攻被盟軍瓦解，部隊遭到重創，損失約10萬兵員。<br />\n<br />\n而被捕德軍特種部隊成員由於身穿美軍軍服，不受日內瓦國際公約保護，兼且觸犯戰爭罪行，被美軍指揮官命令憲兵即場執行槍決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/712822242120609/posts/2436536723082477?s=100010086875474&amp;v=i&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F712822242120609%2Fposts%2F2436536723082477%3Fs%3D100010086875474%26v%3Di%26sfns%3Dmo&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=bdd5352a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/712822242120609/posts/2436536723082477?s=100010086875474&amp;v=i&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"e5874be48d7065d3955a8089fda670eb317576d1","tid":1453340,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d797ee2ff9aa085e8e40ce87ab537f680509a6a","tid":1453340,"uid":284630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:57:07.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"358b3cb5310c9065abca5a19ba8afb2f4d9e15e8","tid":1453340,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"以眼還眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" clas